Link in bio 💻
If you buy my shirts
I won’t have to keep wearing them 😊

node.text:
Life is vastly different from my P.O.V. 👀 
People wanting to take a piece of me regardless how I feel.
I know how to protect my energetic space, but if you try get to close physically and uninvited…The Barbarian will see to it that you don’t disturb my peace 😊🌼✨

node.text: The revolution will be televised…on the internet. 📺⚡️
